-- Manchester City Tops Norwich 6-1 to Close on Premier League Lead
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-04-14T14:18:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-14/manchester-city-tops-norwich-6-1-to-close-on-premier-league-lead.html
Manchester City  beat Norwich 6-1 to
close within two points of Manchester United in English soccer’s
Premier League.  Carlos Tevez had a hat trick as Manchester City won for the
first time in four away games. Sergio Aguero added two goals for
City and Adam Johnson had one, while Andrew Surman scored for
Norwich.  City’s second straight victory moves it to 77 points on the
season. League leader United hosts Aston Villa tomorrow and
visits City on April 30.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  